						<summary>

						<p>States that <hi rend="bold">Kolaniya Kettu-Gaṇḍa</hi> made a gift for the upkeep of a perpetual lamp in the temple of Vāsukiravi-Sōmīśvara of <hi rend="bold">Duttika.</hi> The gift is of <hi rend="italic">manniya-tīṟu</hi> which seems to be a local tax.</p>						

						<p>First Face.</p>						

						</summary>
